VitalDrop-Tech Driven Blood Donation Management System

Developed a full-stack blood management system using Spring Boot (Java) and React.js to enhance the efficiency of blood donor registration, blood bank management, inventory tracking, and donation camp organization. Designed and implemented a secure authentication system with JWT, enabling role-based access control for donors and blood banks. Integrated email notifications for donor confirmations, camp alerts, and low blood inventory warnings. Developed search and filter functionalities to allow users to easily locate blood banks, check inventory availability, and register for donation camps. Designed a responsive and intuitive UI with Redux for state management, ensuring a seamless user experience. Built an analytics dashboard to track donation statistics, blood inventory trends, and camp participation rates, providing valuable insights for better decision-making.
